50
00:05:03,150 --> 00:05:05,084
-Surprised to see me?

51
00:05:12,017 --> 00:05:12,750
-Ninja Art.

52
00:05:12,784 --> 00:05:13,450
Spiral Spiderweb!

53
00:05:19,017 --> 00:05:20,450
-Naruto!

54
00:05:20,484 --> 00:05:21,884
NARUTO (VOICEOVER):
Kiba, Akamaru.

55
00:05:21,917 --> 00:05:23,350
Now's your chance.

56
00:05:23,384 --> 00:05:24,950
When he's in midair
like that, there's

57
00:05:24,984 --> 00:05:27,584
