60
00:05:39,384 --> 00:05:42,384
-You stole my line, punk.

61
00:05:42,417 --> 00:05:44,050
You should look
down at your feet.

62
00:05:47,117 --> 00:05:49,450
-You coward!

63
00:05:49,484 --> 00:05:54,250
