NEJI (VOICEOVER): My turn.

72
00:06:29,784 --> 00:06:30,750
-Neji!

73
00:06:30,784 --> 00:06:31,384
No!

74
00:06:31,417 --> 00:06:32,250
-He'a stuck!

75
00:06:32,284 --> 00:06:33,550
SHIKAMARU (VOICEOVER): Darn it.

76
